♪Feuds and grievances tie my heart♪

244
00:11:36,300 --> 00:11:38,820
♪On a night fraught with peril♪

245
00:11:38,820 --> 00:11:41,300
♪The abyss yawns before my gaze♪

246
00:11:41,300 --> 00:11:43,500
♪Beneath a defiant facade♪

247
00:11:43,500 --> 00:11:45,940
♪Grief is tightly wrapped inside♪

248
00:11:46,100 --> 00:11:48,660
♪Suddenly, a ray of light appears♪

249
00:11:48,660 --> 00:11:51,380
♪Piercing right through my doubts♪

250
00:11:51,380 --> 00:11:55,340
♪And becoming my sun♪

251
00:11:55,860 --> 00:11:58,420
♪You are my light♪

252
00:11:58,420 --> 00:12:00,900
♪Driving away endless darkness♪

253
00:12:00,900 --> 00:12:03,300
♪Guiding me toward what's to come♪

254
