♪You shine upon my path♪

257
00:12:10,700 --> 00:12:14,020
♪Walk this journey with me♪

258
00:12:15,540 --> 00:12:17,140
♪Echoes of time resound♪

259
00:12:17,140 --> 00:12:19,620
♪Each year settles in my heart♪

260
00:12:19,620 --> 00:12:20,740
♪Wherever you are♪

261
